                            <comment id="16778972" author="sdehaes" created="Wed, 27 Feb 2019 06:48:55 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=lucacanali&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;lucacanali&quot;&gt;lucacanali&lt;/a&gt; as a temporary fix I added the layer&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
RUN ln -s /lib64/ld-linux-x86-64.so.2 /lib/ld-linux-x86-64.so.2&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;to&#160;make the image usable&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
